milestones.description: Romaine has scored 4 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for BMUDA breaking David Hemp's record
Tucker and Romaine's 76-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 67 between David Hemp and Tucker
Romaine and Rodney Trott's 49-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 43 between Tucker and Malachi Jones
Romaine has become the top scorer for BMUDA in ODIs with 598 runs, going past Lionel Cann's 543
Tucker has broken the record for most catches (9) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Mukuddem's 8

stories.summary: A bristling 54 from Maurice Ouma and a fearless 34 from Lameck Onyango, who remained unbeaten at the end, took Kenya to a three-wicket win over Bermuda in the second one-dayer at the Gymkhana

stories.title: Ouma and Onyango guide Kenya to series win
stories.subTitle: Kenya v Bermuda, 2nd ODI, Nairobi
stories.summary: A bristling 54 from Maurice Ouma and a fearless 34 from Lameck Onyango, who remained unbeaten at the end, took Kenya to a three-wicket win over Bermuda in the second one-dayer at the Gymkhana
